{"id": "1434827032541397043", "channel_id": "1434827032541397043", "type": 0, "author_id": "704667796021182485", "author_name": "fujiiapples", "author_bot": false, "content": "Hi all, thank you in advance for any help. I'm currently on Chapter 5 and I'm level 28 with the attached teams based on some guides I saw on Discord + Flares guide.\n\nI have the equivalent of ~130 Luminous cores available. Which character/s should I save it for to invest in for short and long-term? Noticed Castor, Tawil and Murphy are available now and potentially a lot more during the anniversary later.\n\nAlso would appreciate any other tips based on my lineups.\n\nThank you!", "timestamp": "2025-11-03T08:50:22.355000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-11-03T09:43:41.203000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1434827033002639442", "filename": "Team_1.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 136477, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1434827032541397043/1434827033002639442/Team_1.jpg?ex=69ccdc4e&is=69cb8ace&hm=f018263d7148c39b44459d47f5e42138eb62536e2461663bfbc151debb617649&"}, {"id": "1434827033753423922", "filename": "Team_2.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 143738, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1434827032541397043/1434827033753423922/Team_2.jpg?ex=69ccdc4e&is=69cb8ace&hm=2b11468df9b53f31edce5190fb3c6b993ca48cecb7b2d1cc94bb47e7718a96e2&"}, {"id": "1434827034277707836", "filename": "Available.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 96226, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1434827032541397043/1434827034277707836/Available.jpg?ex=69ccdc4e&is=69cb8ace&hm=d5b1e6fc86ba9a719511901b3d28ff24b52bcd1d56e810862e8cf1f78e347d18&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1434827032541397043", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "What would you try to pull for next during the Anniversary?", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956", "thread_tags": ["1400747463379390545", "1400747088