{"id": "1434764281949196288", "channel_id": "1434764281949196288", "type": 0, "author_id": "756172812552634529", "author_name": "hina_kanzaki", "author_bot": false, "content": "whats tawils gameplay loop? i got her OE but she seems clunky to use, i think idk how to use her cards effectively. currently running her with caecus hameln ryker", "timestamp": "2025-11-03T04:41:01.448000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1434764281949196288", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Tawil help", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956", "thread_tags": ["1400747489132412979"]}
{"id": "1434779134210478080", "channel_id": "1434764281949196288", "type": 0, "author_id": "756552645661032682", "author_name": "enternameunavailable", "author_bot": false, "content": "You should be fine? It's like, always Pinion first. Unexpected if you don't have Pinion, or use unexpected to grab a wing if needed.\n\nIt's basically Pinion, into draw wings. Exalt if you can to reduce card cost", "timestamp": "2025-11-03T05:40:02.503000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1434764281949196288", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Tawil help", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956", "thread_tags": ["1400747489132412979"]}
